<title>SRI LANKA: Blue Diamonds 12-mth net 10 pct down.</title>
<headline>Blue Diamonds 12-mth net 10 pct down.</headline>
<dateline>COLOMBO 1997-05-29</dateline>
<text>
<p>Unaudited results of Blue Diamonds Jewellery Worldwide Ltd, for the 12 months ended March 31, 1997.</p>
<p>(in millions of rupees unless stated):</p>
<p>				  1997		1996</p>
<p>    Turnover		565.97    vs    860.59</p>
<p>    Net profit	    184.82    vs    204.75</p>
<p>    Tax provision	   --	vs    115.91</p>
<p>NOTE - Blue Diamonds Jewellery manufactures diamond and gem-studded gold jewellery, mainly for export.</p>
<p>-- Colombo newsroom (941) 434319</p>
